  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Your Twisted chakra has found a way to enhance your will. Your ability to push through has virtually tripled, and your ability to push forward with your ambition has also been magnified further.</p><p>You gain the following benefits at all times, even without benefiting from any other Class mod feature:</p><p>• You gain a +2 bonus to all Intelligence, Wisdom, and Charisma Saving throws.<br />• You have a +2 bonus to all Saving throws against Jutsu and Arts with the Fuinjutsu keyword.</p><p>You gain the following benefits while you are under the effects of Desperate Rage or Twisted Chakra Cloak:</p><p>• As a Bonus Action, you may spend 10 Twisted Chakra to immediately end any one Genjutsu effect on you.</p>",
